y**: Extensive use of shadcn-ui with Radix primitives\n\n### Build & Development\n```bash\nnpm install        # Install dependencies\nnpm run dev        # Start dev server (localhost:8080)\nnpm run build      # Production build\nnpm run lint       # ESLint\nnpm run preview    # Preview production build\n```\n\n### Deployment\n- Automated via GitHub Actions on push to `main`\n- Deploys to GitHub Pages\n- Includes SPA fallback for client-side routing\n\n### Current Content\n- One blog post about \".NET 9 Telemetry with OpenTelemetry and HELK\"\n- About page featuring Roberto Serafin's professional bio, tech stack (Vue, React, ASP.NET Core, Azure, K8s, Terraform, etc.), and contact links\n\n### Missing Documentation\nNo `PLANNING.md` or `TASKS.md` files exist in the repository. These would be beneficial for tracking future work and architectural decisions.\n\n---\n\nReady for your next request.",
